Loved this song from outset. But heard it multiple times after being high. This time the voice, the music, poetry all unwrapped the mystery called "love" layer by layer, untill it reached crescendo with the expressive words;
 "Nigah-E-Yar Jise Aashna-E-Raz Kare,
Woh Apni Khoobi-E-Qismat Pe
Kyun Na Naaz Kare".
 Hats off to everyone involved in production of this song.
